[65.806784, "o", "\u001b[38;5;141m\r\n## Enabling Metrics Collection (ServiceMonitor)\r\n\r\nSCONE metrics are exposed via Prometheus and require a ServiceMonitor to be applied before dashboards can display data.\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m"]
