[69.938782, "o", "\u001b[38;5;141m\r\n## Grafana Dashboard\r\n\r\nBefore importing the SCONE dashboards, you must be able to access the Grafana UI.\r\n\r\nThe login credentials for the Grafana dashboard are:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m"]
